\frac{\partial u}{\partial t}= \operatorname{div}\left(a^2 E \nabla u\left(r,\varphi,\psi \right) \right) 
 B_{1}(0)=\left\{x \in \mathbb{R^3}: \left\| x \right\| \le 1 \right\} 
